<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('./partials/head')%>
    <link rel="stylesheet"  href="/public/styles/service.css">
    <title>ServiTrack</title>
    <!-- Add Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-LAav8qGOHp/lWYWq5jpn5qIAWP/p5rj8tAHy4tNqpyIWjpAmM4vjWpL2iZ8QLKgA" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <style>
        /* Sidebar style */
        .sidebar {
            height: 100vh; /* Full height */
            width: 250px; /* Fixed width */
            position: fixed; /* Make sidebar fixed on the left */
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            background-color: #45494e; /* Dark background */
            padding-top: 20px; /* Space at the top */
        }

        .sidebar a {
            padding: 15px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: white;
            display: block;
        }

        .sidebar a:hover {
            background-color: #7d7f81;
        }

        /* Main content */
        .main-content {
            margin-left: 250px; /* Same as the width of the sidebar */
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Fixed navbar */
        .navbar {
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        /* Adjust the main content padding due to fixed navbar */
        .main-content {
            padding-top: 60px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .sidebar {
                position: relative; /* Change to relative on small screens */
                height: auto; /* Allow sidebar to collapse */
                width: 100%; /* Full width */
                display: block; /* Ensure it displays */
            }

            .main-content {
                margin-left: 0; /* Remove left margin on small screens */
                padding: 20px; /* Keep padding */
            }

            .navbar {
                position: relative; /* Change navbar to relative on small screens */
            }
            #emptyLink {
                display: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('./partials/nav')%>

    <div class="sidebar">
        <a id="emptyLink"></a>
        <a href="/service/services">Services</a>
        <a href="/service/book">Book a service</a>
        <a href="/service/serviceHistory">Service History</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Main content -->
    <div class="main-content">
        <h2>Welcome to ServiTrack</h2>
        <p>We offer various vehicle sevices</p>

        <!-- Content that will change when navigating between pages -->
       <!-- Content that will change when navigating between pages -->
<div id="pageContent" class="page-content">
    <h2 class="content-heading">Explore Our Vehicle Services</h2>
    <p>ServiTrack is committed to offering top-notch, reliable vehicle services tailored to your needs. Whether it’s routine maintenance or unexpected repairs, we’re here to keep your vehicle in peak condition.</p>

    <div class="service-list">
        <div class="service-item">
            <h4>Oil Change</h4>
            <p>Ensure your engine runs smoothly with our high-quality oil change service, using only top-grade oils and filters for optimal performance and longevity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item">
            <h4>Vehicle Repairs</h4>
            <p>Our expert mechanics handle all types of repairs, from engine diagnostics to transmission overhauls, ensuring your vehicle is back to peak condition in no time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item">
            <h4>Brake Inspection and Replacement</h4>
            <p>Your safety is our priority. We offer thorough brake inspections and quality brake replacements to ensure dependable braking performance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item">
            <h4>Battery Testing and Replacement</h4>
            <p>Don't get stranded with a dead battery. Our battery testing and replacement service ensures your vehicle has the power it needs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item">
            <h4>Tire Rotation and Balancing</h4>
            <p>Maximize the life of your tires and ensure a smooth ride with our tire rotation and balancing services, recommended every 6,000 miles.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item">
            <h4>Service Booking and Reminders</h4>
            <p>Plan ahead with our easy-to-use booking system. Book services at your convenience, and get timely reminders for your upcoming appointments.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p>At ServiTrack, our goal is to provide high-quality, reliable vehicle services that keep you safe and your vehicle performing at its best.</p>
</div>

    </div>

